doc.after: Amsterdam Airport Schiphol IATA AMS ICAO EHAM is less than 20 minutes by train from Amsterdam Centraal railway station and is also served by domestic and international intercity trains such as Thalys and Intercity Brussel Schiphol is the largest airport in the Netherlands the fourth largest in Europe and the fourteenth largest in the world in terms of passengers It handles about 50 million passengers per year and is the home base of four airlines KLM transavia com Martinair and Arkefly As of 2013 update Schiphol was the sixth busiest airport in the world measured by international passenger numbers 138
